Here is the _Java Tutorial_ on using the _Map_ collection.  
_[The Map Interface (The Java&amp;trade; Tutorials &amp;gt; Collections &amp;gt; Interfaces)](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/collections/interfaces/map.html)_.

Here is a basic example.

```java
Map&lt;String, Integer&gt; map = new HashMap&lt;&gt;();
map.put(&quot;abc&quot;, 123);
map.put(&quot;def&quot;, 456);
