Check again if your Jenkins is really using Java 8 when building your project.

Also, specify maven compiler source and target version to Java 8 in project&#39;s `pom.xml`. 

Either add the properties in `pom.xml`:

    &lt;project&gt;
      [...]
      &lt;properties&gt;
        &lt;maven.compiler.source&gt;1.8&lt;/maven.compiler.source&gt;
        &lt;maven.compiler.target&gt;1.8&lt;/maven.compiler.target&gt;
      &lt;/properties&gt;
      [...]
    &lt;/project&gt;

or configure maven compiler plugin:

    &lt;project&gt;
      [...]
      &lt;build&gt;
        [...]
        &lt;plugins&gt;
          &lt;plugin&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;
