Small information between these elements ant `typedef` vs `taskdef`.

 * **[`Typedef`](https://ant.apache.org/manual/Tasks/typedef.html)**: Using a `typedef` declaration allows you to store the Ant Tasks&#39; library anywhere you like (such as source control) and put it&#39;s location in the build file.

